Text: Reuploaded after a failure. These do not have all the artwork, but Google can fix that. Seed my friends.

And I am serious about buying their stuff. These aren't corporate arseholes doing it for more $$$ in their clutching hands. They're just guys who love their music and hope to make a living out of it. So to keep the albums coming, please, please please buy their albums if you like it.
peace/out
